headline: SMArtX Advisory Solutions Expands Manager Marketplace with 25 New Strategies from Seven Leading Asset Management Firms
summary: SMArtX Advisory Solutions ("SMArtX"), a leading innovator in managed accounts technology, has announced the addition of 25 new strategies from seven leading asset management firms to its Manager Marketplace. SMArtX's continuously growing platform now offers 1,553 strategies from 323 distinguished asset management firms.
